author: Animalogic
description:
The cookiecutter shark is one of the weirdest and least understood sharks in the ocean. It hunts small prey like other small sharks, but it also supplements its diet with large chunks of whale, seal, and large fish meat. How did they evolve to be so weird, and what made them so daring?
